"""
        Test that the inequality operator returns True when comparing two
        CryptographicParameters structs with different digital signature
        algorithms.
        """
a = CryptographicParameters(digital_signature_algorithm=enums.
    DigitalSignatureAlgorithm.DSA_WITH_SHA1)
b = CryptographicParameters(digital_signature_algorithm=enums.
    DigitalSignatureAlgorithm.ECDSA_WITH_SHA1)
self.assertTrue(a != b)
self.assertTrue(b != a)
